Feleke was born as a stray on Lovers Lane as a result of his parents giving their animal instincts. He ties interact with his hedonism and detachment of business alley lane, He became acquainted with six other cats named Coco, Beshadu, Foxy, Hellcat, Nihal and Hanna, a German Shepherd named Genzebe, a Beagle named Penny, and a corn snake named Peppa

In 2018 he moved into new street named Back Lane, an Hedonism street, He wants to mate cats, But Hallow the cat wants to mate with Feleke, he tried but he was unable to ejaculate, When Heavy rain disaster came, He found an defensive base on tree

in 2019 He tried to wander back to Lovers Lane, but he got hit by a car, The impact inverted his paw, fracturing his nose and ripping his stomach, Miraculously, He survived but suffered so much pain for years

In 2022, He went to swim in the sewer, Fortunately, she reached into port, he hopped board the ship ''Eastern Emerald'', After he sneaked into the hiding spot, he fell asleep behind some pillows as the ship starting to set off, When he woke up, He found herself in port of DR Congo, where he sneaked to get off the ship, he started newest life on Lovers Lane,

In 2025, He went into swim in the sewer again, he got injured, which killing him instantly

